.TH ZOPEN-PUBLISH "1" "June 2026" "zopen tools 0.8.5" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
zopen-publish \- manual page for zopen-publish 0.8.5
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B zopen-publish
[\fI\,OPTION\/\fR] \fI\,-p PAX_FILE -m METADATA_FILE -g TAG\/\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
zopen\-publish \- Publish zopen package release to GitHub and/or Pulp.
.IP
zopen\-publish [OPTION] \fB\-\-whl\fR WHL_FILE \fB\-\-pulp\-url\fR URL
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
print this help
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
run in verbose mode.
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-force\fR
Force overwrite release if tag exists.
.TP
\fB\-p\fR, \fB\-\-pax\-file\fR PAX_FILE
Path to the pax.Z file required for GitHub publish
.TP
\fB\-m\fR, \fB\-\-metadata\-file\fR FILE
Path to the metadata.json file required for GitHub publish
.TP
\fB\-g\fR, \fB\-\-tag\fR TAG
Tag name for the release, e.g. DEV_mypackage_12345
.TP
\fB\-r\fR, \fB\-\-repo\fR REPO_URL
GitHub repository URL, optional, overrides metadata.json
.TP
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-description\fR TEXT
Description for the GitHub release
.TP
\fB\-b\fR, \fB\-\-build\-line\fR LINE
Build line: DEV or STABLE
.TP
\fB\-t\fR, \fB\-\-github\-token\fR TOKEN
GitHub token, or set GITHUB_TOKEN
.TP
\fB\-o\fR, \fB\-\-github\-org\fR ORG
GitHub Organization, default: zopencommunity
.TP
\fB\-l\fR, \fB\-\-latest\fR
Mark release as Latest / non\-prerelease
.TP
\fB\-\-pulp\fR
Push RPM artifacts to Pulp repository
.TP
\fB\-\-pulp\-repo\fR REPO
Pulp repository name, default: zopen\-stable or zopen\-dev
.TP
\fB\-w\fR, \fB\-\-whl\fR WHL_FILE
Path to a Python wheel file to publish to Pulp PyPI
.TP
\fB\-\-pulp\-url\fR URL
Pulp PyPI repository URL
.TP
\fB\-\-pulp\-user\fR USER
Pulp username, or set PULP_USER
.TP
\fB\-\-pulp\-password\fR PASS
Pulp password, or set PULP_PASSWORD
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
print version
.SS "Environment Variables:"
.TP
GITHUB_TOKEN
GitHub Personal Access Token
.TP
PULP_URL
Pulp PyPI repository URL
.TP
PULP_USER
Pulp username
.TP
PULP_PASSWORD
Pulp password
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP
zopen\-publish \-f \-p install/mypackage.zos.pax.Z \-m metadata.json \-g DEV_mypackage_12345 \-t <token>
zopen\-publish \-\-whl dist/mypackage\-1.0\-py3\-none\-any.whl \-\-pulp\-url http://host:8080/pypi/zopen/
zopen\-publish \-f \-p install/mypackage.zos.pax.Z \-m metadata.json \-g TAG \-t <token> \-\-pulp
.PP
